data.description: This home was built in 2017 and is move in ready!  Seller to provide $5,000 towards closing costs or to help buy down the rate; whichever the buyer prefers. Open floor plan, formal living room, formal dining room, large great room with stone fireplace and spacious kitchen with granite countertops, island, pantry, gas stove and double ovens.  The dining room has a beautiful, coffered ceiling and wainscotting. Upstairs there are 4 bedrooms.  The primary suite has all the amenities, with soaking tub, separate water closet, separate shower and huge walk-in closet.  The 2nd bedroom also has a private bath and the 3rd & 4th bedrooms have a jack and jill bath.  The home also offers a large lot, fenced-in backyard, extended covered back porch with 2 ceiling fans! Plus there is a community boat ramp right around the corner!  Convenient to everything.  Don't miss this opportunity!
